--SQL SCRIPT RAN IN LAS VIRGENES TO UPDATE METER CUSTOM 1 TO ALLOW NULL VALUES DUE TO THE METER EXCHANGE INTERFACE THROWING ERRORS FOR THE FIELD BEING NULL

